#. type: SH
#, no-wrap
msgid "DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "BESCHREIBUNG"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"B<pause>()  causes the calling process (or thread) to sleep until a signal "
"is delivered that either terminates the process or causes the invocation of "
"a signal-catching function."
msgstr ""
"Der Systemaufruf pause veranläst den aufrufenden Prozess zu warten, bis er "
"das entsprechende Signal zum Weitermachen erhält."

#. type: SH
#, no-wrap
msgid "RETURN VALUE"
msgstr "RÜCKGABEWERT"

#.  .BR ERESTARTNOHAND .
#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"B<pause>()  only returns when a signal was caught and the signal-catching "
"function returned.  In this case B<pause>()  returns -1, and I<errno> is set "
"to B<EINTR>."
msgstr ""
"B<pause> gibt immer -1 zurück.  Außerdem wird I<errno> auf B<ERESTARTNOHAND> "
"gesetzt."

#. type: SH
#, no-wrap
msgid "ERRORS"
msgstr "FEHLER"

